data.description: Come check out this immaculately maintained home on the East side of Austin located just off Slaughter Lane!  You won't want to miss this one.  Situated on a corner lot, this two- story home has space to live/work/play under one roof!  The home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a dedicated home office on the main level with a bonus room/loft on the second story.  The home has recently had a number of upgrades and improvements!  It is truly move-in ready!  Please ask for the upgrades and improvements sheet!  First open house will be on 4/29 from 12:00-2:00!  We look forward to your visit!
